description:
This week on Unqualified Anna and Sim sit down with one of the most recognized comic book icons in history, Stan Lee (Marvel Comics, Fantastic Four, Thor, X-Men, Spider-Man)! The gang talks about human kindness, Stan’s organization "Hands of Respect,” and play a round of Not So Rapid Fire Questions! Then, they call Kayley who is having trouble getting her husband to eat right and work out. 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
